title: Looking for a duo mate to EUEast!
body:
Hello!
I made a new account on Eu-East, i got a lot of experience about the game tho!
Im 24 years old from sweden, i also have a mic!
My goal is to get my new account to level 30 and then do ranked with a duo mate!
Add me if you wanna be that mate! ;D
Add: Zerenadez

replies.body:
Hey friend,

You may want to post this to the [EUNE Teams & Clubs boards](http://boards.eune.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/team-recruitment-en), where you'll find other players centralized to your region and looking to play with others.

Let me know if you have any other questions. ^.^
